Welcome to Zork!

This disk contains all that you need to get Zork up and running on your Apple 
Lisa running UniPlus (System V) Unix.

This disk contains the following files:

FILES:	
		readme      - this file
		install.sh  - the installation script
		zork        - the C source files tarball
		dtextc.dat  - the game database file

SETUP:

	Run the installer script with:
	
	./setup.sh
	
	This will install the Zork executable to /usr/games and the game's data
	file to /usr/games/lib. Once copied, Zork can be run with:
	
	/usr/games/zork